<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak wheat berries for 8 days, changing water daily]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Drain and cook for 15 mins, barely covered in water, then drain on low heat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Boil wheat in milk, cinnamon, lemon zest, pinch of salt on low heat until all liquid is absorbed, 2h]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Discard the lemon zest and spread on a plate to cool]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Mix ricotta, sugar, cinnamon powder, lemon zest, orange blossom water, candied peels in a bowl]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add the egg yolks one at the time, and add the wheat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Beat the egg whites to snowy peaks and add]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Sieve the flour, dry yeast, then make a well]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add butter, egg yolks, sugar one at the time and mix, with cold hands as quickly as possible. Leave to raise for 30m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Roll out in two discs - one to line a 24cm baking tray, which you'll then fill with the filling, and from the other obtain 7 1cm strips which you'll criss cross on top]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Bake 1.5 hours at 180Â°]]></step>
